org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.adapter

Class BasicDataTypeAdapter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.adapter.AbstractDataTypeAdapter<T>
      • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.adapter.BasicDataTypeAdapter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the data type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Persistable, DataTypeAdapter<T>, DataReader<Object>, DataWriter<Object>

    public class BasicDataTypeAdapter<T>
extends AbstractDataTypeAdapter<T>
    A data type adapter implementation with explicit mappings for accessors and mutators. These mappings can be automatically inferred from annotations or public properties via the static `newAdapter` method.
